Value Add 
Package Description
com.thomsonreuters.upa.valueadd.cache
This package contains the UPA Value Add Cache.
com.thomsonreuters.upa.valueadd.common
This package provides common classes for the Value Add Reactor.
com.thomsonreuters.upa.valueadd.domainrep.rdm
This package provides common classes and interfaces for the RDM specific Domain Representations.
com.thomsonreuters.upa.valueadd.domainrep.rdm.dictionary
The RDM Dictionary package is intended to assist developers with encoding and decoding messages used by the Dictionary Reuters Domain Model.
com.thomsonreuters.upa.valueadd.domainrep.rdm.directory
The RDM Directory package is intended to assist developers with encoding and decoding messages used by the Directory Reuters Domain Model.
com.thomsonreuters.upa.valueadd.domainrep.rdm.login
The RDM Login package is intended to assist developers with encoding and decoding messages used by the Login Reuters Domain Model.
com.thomsonreuters.upa.valueadd.domainrep.rdm.queue
The RDM Queue package is intended to assist developers with encoding and decoding messages used by the Queue Reuters Domain Model.

This package provides functionality shared by Value Add examples.

This package contains the UPA Value Add Consumer.
